 The bear bot walked through the cold. It didnt bother him much bec of his 
nice fur coat. He walked to where the pred signature was. He saw what looked 
like megatron letting some bot into his base. he ran up yelling as he went. 
"My name is polartron I am here to serve you." he stopped right in front of 
his bowed his head.
